<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.4.6">
<l>piṉṉiṉṟa kātaṉōy neñcam peritaṭumāṉ</l>
<l>muṉṉiṉ ṟirāvūḻi kaṇputaiya mūṭiṟṟāṉ</l>
<l>maṉṉiṉṟa cakkarattem māyavaṉum vārāṉā</l>
<l>linniṉṟa nīḷāvi kāppārā rivviṭattē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Love sickness that stands behind just kills [my] heart.</l>
<l>Impending night, an aeon, veils off [my] eyes.</l>
<l>Our Dark one too, with [his] lasting discus, will not come.</l>
<l>Who will guard my soul, that long stays here(?), in this place?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
